info.author: Valery Brinnel
info.description:
# ZTF support for AMPEL

ZTF-specific implementations for Ampel such as: - An _AlertSupplier_ compatible with IPAC generated alerts - Shaper classes for ingestion - Encoding utilities for ZTF names (AMPEL requires integer ids) - Classes for archiving alerts
info.name: ampel-ztf
info.summary: Zwicky Transient Facility support for the Ampel system
